# Full Stack Web Application - Spring Boot + React

This project is a full-stack web application built using **Spring Boot** (backend) and **React.js** (frontend). It demonstrates how to build and connect a RESTful API with a modern frontend interface.

## ðŸ’¡ Features

- User registration and authentication
- CRUD operations using RESTful APIs
- React frontend with responsive UI
- Spring Boot backend with JPA and Hibernate
- MySQL/PostgreSQL database integration (configurable)
- Cross-origin communication enabled via CORS

